# 📦 Postal Route Expo App

This is a prototype mobile app built with **React Native + Expo** to help postal workers scan parcels/letters, capture addresses, and build efficient delivery routes.

---

## ✨ Features
- 📷 Capture address labels using the **camera** (OCR placeholder).
- 📦 Scan barcodes with the **barcode scanner**.
- 📝 Manage stops and mark parcels as **delivered**.
- 📍 Location tracking & notifications (proximity alerts).
- 💾 Data persistence (your stops are saved on the device).

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Install Prerequisites
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (LTS version)
- [Expo Go](https://expo.dev/client) on your Android or iOS device
- Git (if you want to clone instead of downloading)

### 2. Clone the Repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/christophermbyrne38/C.Byrne-An-post.git
cd C.Byrne-An-post
